data.description: Where to begin when describing this gorgeous home?! You really have to see it in person to appreciate all it has to offer BUT we will try! Quiet neighborhood with a wonderful community and no through traffic, updated throughout, EVEN the pantry has been upgraded and customized, open layout downstairs perfect for entertaining, ample counter space, huge dining room with seating for 12, downstairs bedroom AND full bathroom right across from it, cute mudroom with shelves and hangers, four bedrooms PLUS a loft upstairs along with upstairs laundry, two spacious closets in the primary bedroom, spacious tub and separate shower! Recently installed 36,000 gallon in-ground smart pool with lighting and a 20 foot sun ledge, the back yard is big enough for the pool AND two play sets AND plenty of green space!***Grass shown was photo shopped because pool was installed last year. We wanted to show what it could look like in the Spring / Summer* CALL TODAY FOR A PRIVATE SHOWING YOU'RE GOING TO LOVE IT!
